# Local Wiki

For this project, read and follow [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) at the project root before any wiki operation (ingest, query, lint, or edits under `wiki/`).

- Never modify files in `raw/`
- Always update `wiki/index.md` and `wiki/log.md` after wiki changes
- Use the page format, log header format, and categorized index described in AGENTS.md
